					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">Think of an open bus read as returning the lowest byte of the address, which it usually does.<br />So it reads from the reset vector, FFFC and FFFD and jumps to FDFC. Then it executes instruction FC (NOP abs,x). Then PC = FDFF, and it executes FF (ISB abs, x). Then it's at FE02, and executes 02 (CPU jam).</div>

					
